the writing of the Philippines

00:08:15.970 --> 00:08:19.820
where my parents are from, what
I realized very quickly was

00:08:19.820 --> 00:08:22.540
that writers were writers
and they wrote everything.

00:08:22.540 --> 00:08:25.530
They wrote novels, they wrote
poems, they were journalists,

00:08:25.530 --> 00:08:27.220
they were speech
writers for politicians

00:08:27.220 --> 00:08:31.010
and so this whole sort of
market division between,

00:08:31.010 --> 00:08:34.040
between genres is not universal.

00:08:34.040 --> 00:08:35.610
It's actually an invention.

00:08:35.610 --> 00:08:38.790
And the other reason why it's a
little bit confounding to me is

00:08:38.790 --> 00:08:42.900
that I came to books
late in life.

00:08:42.900 --> 00:08:47.770
