a college flunky twice over

00:08:47.770 --> 00:08:52.460
and so my original
love was music.

00:08:52.460 --> 00:08:56.580
I wanted to be a
composer and a musician.

00:08:56.580 --> 00:09:03.320
I think of all of writing as
an extension really of music.

00:09:03.320 --> 00:09:07.210
