that's you know, again,

01:07:00.310 --> 01:07:01.760
we can identify it
when it happens.

01:07:01.760 --> 01:07:04.170
I think everyone knows what
I'm talking about here.

01:07:04.170 --> 01:07:06.360
You don't always find
that in a good novel.

01:07:06.360 --> 01:07:09.310
You'll probably always
find it in a good poem.

