01:13:22.060 --> 01:13:26.540
for a very longtime
in western culture,

01:13:26.540 --> 01:13:30.910
and what we really know is the
fact is that the spoken word,

01:13:30.910 --> 01:13:34.070
the singing word, the bodies
among bodies making literature

01:13:34.070 --> 01:13:36.960
and stories and song
is much, much older

01:13:36.960 --> 01:13:38.440
and there's a return to that.

01:13:38.440 --> 01:13:40.840
Somebody much smarter than
that coined a phrase called

01:13:40.840 --> 01:13:44.350
"The new orality" with the
Internet and performance

01:13:44.350 --> 01:13:48.830
and so forth and I know a very
